---
import SiteLayout from "../../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Bail Bonds | PoliceConduct.org"
  pagePath="/partner/bail-bonds/"
>
  <main class="flex-grow-1">
    <section class="py-vh-3 bg-gray-100 border-bottom border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
          <ol class="breadcrumb mb-3">
            <li class="breadcrumb-item">
              <a class="link-dark" href="/partner/">Partners</a>
            </li>
            <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">
              Bail Bonds
            </li>
          </ol>
        </nav>
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-end">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
            <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-2">
              Value proposition
            </p>
            <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold">Bail Bonds Strategic Benefits</h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted mb-0">
              Reduce risk, modernize intake, and keep clients engaged with the
              process.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <div class="text-uppercase small text-muted">Built for</div>
                <div class="fw-semibold">Bail bond agencies</div>
                <div class="text-muted small">
                  Strong documentation lowers flight risk and improves case
                  outcomes.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-7">
            <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold">1. Risk management</h2>
            <p class="text-muted">
              Bail agencies lose money when cases stall or clients feel
              abandoned. Better documentation leads to better legal outcomes,
              which keeps clients engaged and appearing in court.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mb-0 d-flex flex-column gap-2">
              <li>
                Guide clients to capture officer names, badge numbers, and
                timelines.
              </li>
              <li>
                Support defense counsel with structured evidence from day one.
              </li>
              <li>
                Reduce flight risk by keeping clients focused on their case.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-3">
                <div class="text-uppercase small text-muted">Bottom line</div>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  A client with a strong defense is more likely to stay in the
                  system and make court dates.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2 bg-light border-top border-bottom border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">2. Modern intake resource</h2>
        <div class="row g-4">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  PoliceConduct Case Start
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Give families a survival kit</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Provide a structured portal so families can document arrest
                  details while they wait for release.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-6">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Client support
                </p>
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold">Differentiate your agency</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Offer more than funding by giving families a clear next step
                  and a head start for their defense team.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">3. The 2026 compliance hook</h2>
        <p class="text-muted">
          New transparency laws like CA SB 805 require plainclothes officers to
          display ID. Our reporting prompts capture uniform and identification
          details that can surface legal errors quickly.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2 bg-gray-100 border-top border-dark">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-3">4. Bail bonds strategic benefits</h2>
        <div class="table-responsive">
          <table class="table table-bordered align-middle">
            <thead class="table-light">
              <tr>
                <th scope="col">Feature</th>
                <th scope="col">Benefit to the agency</th>
                <th scope="col">Benefit to the client</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Independent reporting</strong></td>
                <td>Reduces liability for giving legal advice.</td>
                <td
                  >Safe, timestamped reporting without retaliation pressure.</td
                >
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Systemic pattern tracking</strong></td>
                <td>Avoid problem precincts with recurring issues.</td>
                <td>Connects incidents to broader accountability efforts.</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td><strong>Case update alerts</strong></td>
                <td>Stay informed when new evidence appears.</td>
                <td>Keeps clients engaged and focused on court dates.</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row g-4 align-items-start">
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
            <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-0 border-dark h-100">
              <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column gap-2">
                <p class="text-uppercase small text-muted mb-1">
                  Partner resource kit
                </p>
                <h2 class="h5 fw-semibold mb-0">Tools for bail agents</h2>
                <p class="text-muted mb-0">
                  Assets that support client intake and reduce risk.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12 col-lg-8">
            <div class="d-flex flex-column gap-3">
              <div class="border-start border-dark ps-3">
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">Client intake flyer</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  A printable QR code flyer that guides families to document the
                  arrest for their defense team.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-start border-dark ps-3">
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">Transparency badge</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  A Partner for Accountability seal for your window or website.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="border-start border-dark ps-3">
                <h3 class="h6 fw-semibold mb-1">Monell liability alerts</h3>
                <p class="mb-0">
                  Alerts when multiple clients report issues in the same jail or
                  precinct, helping you adjust risk assessments.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-vh-2">
      <div class="container">
        <div
          class="d-flex flex-column flex-lg-row align-items-lg-center justify-content-between gap-3"
        >
          <div>
            <h2 class="h4 fw-semibold mb-1">Ready to modernize bail intake?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted mb-0">
              We can share a bail agent referral script to use with families at
              release.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            class="btn btn-dark rounded-0"
            href="/about/contact?whoami=Partner&message=I%27m%20interested%20in%20a%20bail%20agent%20referral%20script%20and%20partner%20kit."
          >
            Request the referral script
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</SiteLayout>
